ia e comp\u00ec viaggi di esplorazione sulle Alpi."]], "wiki_links": [{"item": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1693772", "itemLabel": "Johann Georg Altmann", "dhsid": "010500", "namefr": "Johann Georg Altmann", "articlefr": "https://fr.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johann_Georg_Altmann", "namede": "Johann Georg Altmann", "articlede": "https://de.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johann_Georg_Altmann", "nameit": "", "articleit": "", "nameen": "", "articleen": "", "instanceof": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q5", "instanceofLabel": "\u00eatre humain", "gndid": "117761419"}], "wikidata_url": "http://www.wikidata.org/entity/Q1693772", "wikipedia_page_title": null, "added_wikidata_wikipedia_to_text_links": true, "_initial": null, "url": "https://hls-dhs-dss.ch/it/articles/010500/2001-05-21"}